===Talk to Hysilens{{subst:void|<!--104050403-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=trailblaze|location=The 1st Eternal Recurrence: Dawncloud During Doomsday|update|Do you still remember them, Khaslana, the one who won't reach the dawn?<br />The hero tore through the sky, the Holy Maiden fell from the cliff, and the chessmaster ignited the first Flame, all in the name of prophecy of Worldbearer.<br />What noble deeds! And yet fate, ever generous, ensures that the death-bound nymphs shall find their death nevertheless.<br />O Deliverer, behold the lifeless ash they've become! Do you still futilely dream of saving them?<br />Those who push the boulder upward will see the earth swallow them whole. Those who meddle with time earn nothing but a shattered shell.<br />Hear me. You're no different from them: The singers still scream, and the bright-eyed still go blind.<br />Go, then! March on alone &mdash;<br />Revel, dance, throw yourself into the tireless flame, and never stop!}}
